      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC indicates how to obtain various protocol documents used in the DARPA research community.  Included is an overview of the new 1985 DDN Protocol Handbook and available sources for obtaining related documents (such as DOD, ISO, and CCITT).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
